        <mxCell id="server-go" parent="backend-api" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#000000;" value="internal/api/server.go (250 lines)&#xa;• Gin router with CORS middleware&#xa;• POST /api/models - Save model&#xa;• GET /api/models - List models&#xa;• GET /api/models/:id - Get model&#xa;• POST /api/models/:id/run - Execute optimization&#xa;• GET /api/jobs/:id - Job status&#xa;• GET /api/jobs/:id/results - Job results&#xa;• GET /api/osm/:layer - GeoServer data&#xa;• GET /api/osm/layers - Available layers&#xa;• GET /api/health - Health check" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="580" x="10" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
